oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Dalāʼil al-khayrāt , 1228 H. : manuscript codex
دلائل الخيرات
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Original slipcase removed for preservation. Both case and manuscript now housed in clamshell case.

Nine lines of text (black and occasional red ink) per page, enclosed in gold border, with second gold border enclosing facing pages; catchwords and other text between borders. Two miniatures depicting the most holy mosques on facing leaves. Additional gold leaf decoration within text.
